the colossus of maroussi is an impressionist travelogue by henry miller which was first published in 1941 by colt press of san francisco .

literary greece : ( cheryl of the clue crew delivers the clue from santorini , greece . )   he wrote in 1941 's " the colossus of maroussi " that , " in greece , light penetrates to the soul , opens the doors and windows of the heart "

